<body>
<div><head>《秦子》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.2">欲顯白于雪中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.3">馳光于日下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.4">不可得也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.5">馬總《意林》卷五、歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.6">顧彥先難云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.7">有味如醽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.8">而不醉人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.9">其味如黍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.10">飲之則醉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.11">何也？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.12">秦子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.13">醉在小人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.14">不在君子；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.15">吾欲錦中而紵表，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.16">不欲繡外而麻裏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.17">猶論者寧匱于辭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.18">不匱于理。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-1a.19">《意林》卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.2">遠難知者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.3">天；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.4">近難知者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.5">人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.6">《意林》卷五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.7">因斧以得柯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.8">因柯以成；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.9">用種一粟則千萬之粟滋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-2a.10">種一仁則眾行之美備矣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.2">鍼雖小，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.3">入水則沈；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.4">毛雖大，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.5">入水則浮。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.6">性自然也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.7">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.8">有千金之裘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.9">而無千金之布。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-3a.10">《北堂書鈔》卷一百二十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.2">今人知涉川必溺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.3">而忘酒醴之荒性。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.4">《北堂書鈔》卷一百四十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.5">秦子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.6">常問作人當如園圃之藍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.7">不異眾草，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.8">染而後朗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.9">然不如唐棣之華，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.10">灼灼自顯。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-4a.11">《藝文類聚》卷八十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.2">孔文舉為北海相，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.3">有遭父喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.4">哭泣墓側，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.5">色無憔悴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.6">文舉殺之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.7">又有母病瘥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.8">思食新麥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.9">家無，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.10">乃盜鄰熟麥而進之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.11">文舉聞之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.12">特賞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.13">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.14">無有來討，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.15">勿復盜也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.16">盜而不罪者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.17">以為勤於母飢；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.18">哭而見殺者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.19">以為形慈而心否。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-5a.20">《藝文類聚》卷八十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.2">一人執規，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.3">十手自員；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.4">一人吹簫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.5">長短皆應。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.6">《太平御覽》卷五百八十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.7">五味者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.8">各稱一族之名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.9">合和一鼎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.10">名曰羹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.11">猶威重廉平，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.12">恩合而為信也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-6a.13">《太平御覽》卷八百六十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.2">智惠多則引血氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.3">如燈火消暗膏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.4">炷大而朗朗則膏消，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.5">炷小而闇闇則息膏則久也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.6">《太平御覽》卷八百七十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.7">虎能雄猛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.8">不可以託麑；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.9">鷹能飄擊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.10">不可以寄雛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.11">《太平御覽》卷九百六，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-7a.12">又卷九百二十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.2">踰枳棘之籬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.3">則有絓柱之患；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.4">登椒樹之圃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.5">則有榮華之芳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.6">《太平御覽》卷九百五十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.7">食瓜者雖去蔕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.8">何以連其根？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-8a.9">《太平御覽》卷九百七十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.2">玉壺必求其所以盛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.3">干將必求其所以斷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.4">《文選‧鮑明遠白頭吟》李善注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.5">無盛之卮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.6">雖赤瓊碧瓐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.7">無貴也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.8">不斷之劍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.9">雖含影承光，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.10">無取也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1475_CHANT_001-9a.11">楊慎《丹鉛總錄》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
